title: Drag Race Philippines: Slaysian Royale
overview: Filipino pride meets global drag excellence in the fiercest drag showdown of the year! Twelve dazzling queens battle for the crown to become the very first Slaysian Royalty. With next-level drama, jaw-dropping talent, and unapologetic Asian artistry, this season serves Asian representation like never before. Get ready to slay, the Slaysian Royale way!
